feat(auth)!: :sparkles: replace jwt lib

Why:
The jsonwebtoken library has known CVEs and lacks native
TypeScript types. jose is standards-compliant and provides
full TS support with zero native dependencies.

What:
Migrate all token signing/verification from jsonwebtoken to
jose library. Update jwt.ts, middleware.ts, types.ts, and
package.json to use jose SignJWT builder pattern and
jwtVerify() with explicit algorithm allowlist.

BREAKING CHANGE: JWT tokens signed with jsonwebtoken are incompatible with jose. All active sessions will be invalidated. Users must log in again after deployment.
